    "en": {
      "name": "Centur-Ion Cimelia",
      "effect": "When your opponent activates a monster effect as Chain Link 2 or higher (Quick Effect): You can activate this effect; the activated effect becomes \"Your opponent places 1 \"Centur-Ion\" monster from their face-up field or GY in their Spell & Trap Zone as a face-up Continuous Trap\", also you cannot Special Summon \"Centur-Ion Cimelia\" for the rest of this turn. During the Main Phase, if this card is a Continuous Trap: You can Special Summon this card. You can only use each effect of \"Centur-Ion Cimelia\" once per turn.",
      "official": false
    },
